ü§ù 6. Optional Group Activity (Advanced)
Title: ‚ÄúPitch the Prompt‚Äù

Objective:
Each group picks a scenario (e.g., joint AI grant, startup collaboration) ‚Üí writes 2 prompts ‚Üí tests them in Claude and ChatGPT ‚Üí presents outputs and discusses which worked better and why.
